!07_LOGS/Build-Logs/
!07_LOGS/Build-Logs/Build-Logs-Index.example.md
!07_LOGS/Daily/
!07_LOGS/Daily/Daily-Index.example.md

99_ARCHIVE/**
!99_ARCHIVE/README.md
!99_ARCHIVE/Documentation-History/
!99_ARCHIVE/Documentation-History/Documentation-History-Index.example.md

docs/**
